Valgrind is a tool to detect memory leaks in your programs. We will go through simple examples to show how to read the output from Valgrind in simple context.

Things it can detect:
1. Dangling pointers
2. Memory leaks
3. Uninitialized data
4. Writing past array boundary

Valgrind homepage:
http://www.valgrind.org/

